Ok, I'll bite. What exactly would you propose in terms of changes that we could be so excellent as to not even miss a critical utility skill?<br>
<br>
Imho, it really needs to be something more than damage because turning a class into a one-trick pony isn't going to help. Ok, a two-trick pony since we'd still be able to port. Currently, groups have a wide and varied selection of damage dealers all of which provide some type of additional utility or benefit to the group.<br>
<br>
Tal<br>
